# Writing [rainbow]Marquee[/rainbow], as itself

This page is [WRITING.md](WRITING.md) turned inside out: **every demo comes twice — first the
markup you'd type (in a code fence), then the same markup, live.** The source of this very
document is the full worked example. Preview it from `ts/html_renderer`:

```
npm run preview -- ../../WRITING.mq > tour.html
```

## Paragraphs and line breaks

```marquee
This paragraph is written
across several source lines,
and none of those breaks survive — it flows.

Roses are red\
violets are blue,\
these lines end in backslashes\
so each one renders new.
```

