violets are blue,\
these lines end in backslashes\
so each one renders new.

## Headings

```marquee
### A heading with *emphasis*, [color=goldenrod]color[/color], and [blink]blink[/blink]

####### Seven hashes is just a paragraph, rendered literally.
```

### A heading with *emphasis*, [color=goldenrod]color[/color], and [blink]blink[/blink]

